#~| "Haven’t you ever found a tool that was perfect for your need but you "
#~| "only found it after some time stumbling upon it on the net? When "
#~| "considering to install an application, don’t you wonder sometimes if "
#~| "it’s really worth it? Or if it’s actually what you’re looking for?"
#~ msgid ""
